# 2. Complete Architecture VM + OTel for LLM

## 2.1 Overview

The architecture below covers the full metrics collection path from LLM sources to dashboards and alerts. It is deployable in full air-gap mode.

![](./media/image1.png)

*Diagram 1 : Complete VictoriaMetrics architecture for LLM observability - air-gap compatible*

> **Key architectural points**
>
> All sources emit to the OTel Collector via OTLP (gRPC port 4317 or HTTP port 4318)
>
> The Collector filters, enriches (k8s labels), derives metrics from traces (spanmetrics), and exports
>
> VictoriaMetrics receives via Remote Write. In Single mode, it also accepts OTLP directly.
>
> VMAlert evaluates MetricsQL rules and sends alerts to Alertmanager
>
> Grafana uses VictoriaMetrics as a datasource (Prometheus-compatible, zero reconfiguration)
>
> vmanomaly (Enterprise) adds ML-based anomaly detection on LLM metrics

## 2.2 Components and roles

| **Component**          | **Port(s)**              | **Role for LLM observability**                                                  |
|------------------------|--------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| OTel Collector         | 4317 (gRPC), 4318 (HTTP) | Normalises and routes all metrics. spanmetrics derives metrics from RAG traces. |
| VictoriaMetrics Single | 8428                     | TSDB storage, MetricsQL API, Remote Write, direct OTLP, built-in vmui           |
| vmagent                | 8429                     | Distributed Prometheus scraping. Ideal for DCGM Exporter, vLLM /metrics, Ollama |
| vmalert                | 8880                     | Evaluation of MetricsQL alert rules. Talks to Alertmanager.                     |
| Alertmanager           | 9093                     | Alert routing: Slack, PagerDuty, email, webhook. Deduplication and silencing.   |
| Grafana                | 3000                     | Dashboards. Uses the VictoriaMetrics plugin or standard Prometheus datasource.  |
| vmanomaly (Enterprise) | 9090                     | ML anomaly detection (ARIMA, Prophet) on LLM metrics. Optional.                 |

