| \# Via API: http://victoriametrics:8428/api/v1/status/tsdb |
|                                                            |
| \# Top 10 metrics by cardinality (MetricsQL)               |
| topk(10, count by (\_\_name\_\_) ({\_\_name\_\_!=""}))     |

